<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Reconcile File Editor Test Cases</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 20px;
            line-height: 1.4;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            color: #333333;
        }
        .test-case {
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .test-case.failure-case {
            border-color: #ff9800;
        }
        .test-header {
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
            padding: 15px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;
        }
        .test-case.failure-case .test-header {
            background-color: #fff3e0;
        }
        .test-title {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin: 0;
            color: #333;
        }
        .test-name {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #666;
            margin: 5px 0 0 0;
            font-family: monospace;
        }
        .test-description {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #555;
            margin: 8px 0 0 0;
        }
        .test-content {
            padding: 15px;
        }
        .params {
            background-color: #f0f0f0;
            padding: 10px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
            font-size: 13px;
        }
        .params-title {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #666;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .file-comparison {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 15px;
        }
        .file-column {
            padding: 0;
        }
        .column-header {
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            color: #666;
            font-size: 14px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        }
        .content {
            background-color: #f8f8f8;
            padding: 12px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
            font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
            font-size: 12px;
            line-height: 1.5;
            white-space: pre;
            overflow-x: auto;
            margin: 0;
        }
        .line-number {
            display: inline-block;
            width: 25px;
            color: #999;
            text-align: right;
            margin-right: 10px;
            user-select: none;
        }
        .target-line {
            background-color: #fff3e0;
            display: block;
            margin: 0 -12px;
            padding: 0 12px;
            border-left: 3px solid #ff9800;
        }
        .changed-line {
            background-color: #e8f5e9;
            display: block;
            margin: 0 -12px;
            padding: 0 12px;
            border-left: 3px solid #4caf50;
        }
        h1 {
            color: #333;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #0066cc;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .summary {
            background-color: #e8f4f8;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            border-left: 4px solid #0066cc;
        }
        .summary h2 {
            margin-top: 0;
            color: #0066cc;
        }
        .failure-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #ff9800;
            color: white;
            font-size: 11px;
            padding: 2px 6px;
            border-radius: 3px;
            margin-left: 10px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }
        .legend {
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            padding: 10px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            font-size: 12px;
        }
        .target-indicator {
            background-color: #fff3e0;
            padding: 2px 4px;
            border-radius: 2px;
            border-left: 3px solid #ff9800;
        }
        .changed-indicator {
            background-color: #e8f5e9;
            padding: 2px 4px;
            border-radius: 2px;
            border-left: 3px solid #4caf50;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>Reconcile File Editor Test Cases</h1>

    <div class="summary">
        <h2>What This Shows</h2>
        <p>Tests for the file editor that updates reconciliation status markers in ledger files.</p>
        <p><strong>Features tested:</strong></p>
        <ul>
            <li>Updating posting statuses (uncleared → pending → cleared)</li>
            <li>Smart normalization (using transaction headers when all postings have same status)</li>
            <li>Precondition validation (checking expected current status before updating)</li>
            <li>Error handling for invalid line numbers and edge cases</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="legend">
            <strong>Legend:</strong>
            <span class="target-indicator">Target posting lines</span> |
            <span class="changed-indicator">Changed lines</span>
        </div>
        <p><strong>Test cases:</strong> {{totalTestCases}}</p>
    </div>

{{#each testCases}}
    <div class="test-case {{#unless config.test_params.expected_result}}failure-case{{/unless}}">
        <div class="test-header">
            <h3 class="test-title">{{title}}{{#unless config.test_params.expected_result}}<span class="failure-badge">Expected Failure</span>{{/unless}}</h3>
            <p class="test-name">test/data/reconcile-file-editor/{{name}}/</p>
            {{#if config.description}}
            <p class="test-description">{{config.description}}</p>
            {{/if}}
        </div>
        <div class="test-content">
            <div class="params">
                <div class="params-title">Test Parameters</div>
                <div>posting_line_numbers: [{{join config.test_params.posting_line_numbers ", "}}]</div>
                <div>expected_current_status: "{{config.test_params.expected_current_status}}"</div>
                <div>new_status: "{{config.test_params.new_status}}"</div>
                <div>expected_result: {{config.test_params.expected_result}}</div>
            </div>
            <div class="file-comparison">
                <div class="file-column">
                    <div class="column-header">Input (input.ledger)</div>
                    <pre class="content">{{{highlightLines input config.test_params.posting_line_numbers "target"}}}</pre>
                </div>
                <div class="file-column">
                    <div class="column-header">Expected (expected.ledger)</div>
                    <pre class="content">{{{highlightDiff input expected config.test_params.posting_line_numbers}}}</pre>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
{{/each}}

</body>
</html>
